reviewText: Bought for my sister who loves it!

Here are The Cocaine Fiends and Reefer Madness packaged together in a double feature from our friends at Legend Films. This DVD even includes the standard commercials and don't forget the concession stand!! Choose your favorite movie watching treat be it popcorn, a giant soda or box candy, and get ready to be entertained. Reefer Madness is such a cult classic and for me I could not help but laugh. My husband loved this one as well. Good date night DVD!!
